msgstr "https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-java/releases/tag/v1.0.0.Alpha2[GitHub のリリースノート]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _posts/2026-02-12-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-samples/tree/main/samples/java/agents[A2A Java SDK Samples]"
msgstr "https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-samples/tree/main/samples/java/agents[A2A Java SDK サンプル]"

